= Route to Ítaca - An Alternate History

It's hard to classify this work. What am I modding from? Formally it is a fork from <a class="link" href="https://red-autumn.itch.io/petrograd-1917">Petrograd 1917</a>, but it clearly takes a lot form the  <a class="link" href="https://originn0.github.io/dynamic_social_democracy/">Dynamic Social Democracy</a> mod and, by extension, from the original <a class="link" href="https://red-autumn.itch.io/social-democracy">Social Democracy, an Alternate History</a> game. It could have been a fork from that amazing mod for all that matters.

In any case, if you're lost or confused on what's this about, do check the info here.

