@bug_report

= Bug Reporting

If you encounter any bugs, issues, typos, or whatever other issue that bothers you, please report them via <a class="link" href="https://github.com/broken-arrows/route_to_itaca/issues">GitHub Issues</a>. If you don't have a GitHub account, you can also contact me via Reddit DM at <a class="link" href="https://www.reddit.com/user/broken_arrows_/">u/broken_arrows_</a>.

If you believe you found a game-breaking bug, please include as much information as possible, like:
- A detailed description of the bug/issue.
- Steps to reproduce it, if applicable.
- Your current save file (if possible).
- Your game version (shown at the main menu).

Any and all reports are most welcome!

